help you out here.

07:02.067 --> 07:05.533
I had a huge monster hit
back in the early '90s.

07:05.633 --> 07:08.967
Ring any bells?

07:09.067 --> 07:10.367
- You're the guy
with the mullet.

07:10.467 --> 07:11.467
