Kentucky Waterfalls,
Missouri Compromise,

07:15.133 --> 07:16.433
Tennessee Top Hat.

07:16.533 --> 07:18.133
Anyway, I'm not here
about my hair.

07:18.233 --> 07:21.367
Uh, I got a killer new band,
killer tunes.

07:21.467 --> 07:23.633
And we wanna debut
our songs here.

07:23.733 --> 07:27.500
- Uh...sure.

07:27.600 --> 07:29.800
What you're gonna wanna do is,

07:29.900 --> 07:31.600
uh, go ahead
and call up the office.

07:31.700 --> 07:34.067
They will set you up
with an audition.

07:34.100 --> 07:36.700
And then if you do well there,
I'll book you a slot

07:36.800 --> 07:40.500
as soon as one opens up,
which basically never happens.

07:40.600 --> 07:42.500
- That's not
gonna work for me, Todd.

07:42.600 --> 07:44.433
I mean,
I already promised my band

07:44.533 --> 07:45.500
we're playing here tonight.

07:45.600 --> 07:47.100
- You promised them?

07:47.200 --> 07:48.133
Uh, what am I thinking?

07:48.233 --> 07:49.267
What am I thinking?

07:49.367 --> 07:50.733
Damn.

07:50.833 --> 07:52.233
You know what I'm thinking?

07:52.333 --> 07:53.367
That's a bummer.

07:53.467 --> 07:57.600
You'll wait your turn
like everybody else.

07:57.700 --> 07:59.400
- Care I use your restroom
before I go?

07:59.500 --> 08:00.533
- Yeah.

08:00.633 --> 08:02.267
Go ahead.

08:02.367 --> 08:03.500
- Alright.

08:03.600 --> 08:05.400
- It's the one with the nametag
bathroom on it.

08:05.500 --> 08:06.833
- Alright, thank you.

08:06.933 --> 08:10.067
- [zipper zips]
- [toilet flushes]

08:10.167 --> 08:13.267
- VERNON: [sighs]

08:13.367 --> 08:16.867
- You know, normally,
I wouldn't say this...

08:16.967 --> 08:19.833
but you need
to drop the soap, man.

08:19.933 --> 08:22.167
You know what I'm sayin'?

08:22.267 --> 08:23.433
- Not really.

08:23.533 --> 08:25.600
- [toilet flushes]

08:25.700 --> 08:27.067
- You hear that sound?

