and muddle.

09:05.267 --> 09:07.767
- Geesh, it takes like an hour
to make a damn drink.

09:07.867 --> 09:10.500
- [laughing]

09:10.600 --> 09:12.133
- Thanks for cheering me up.

09:12.233 --> 09:14.467
And you're the only one
who remembered my birthday.

09:16.533 --> 09:18.600
- Today is your birthday.

09:18.700 --> 09:19.967
- DEBBIE: It's fine.
