09:32.267 --> 09:34.767
- I'm gonna need
everybody to calm down!

09:34.867 --> 09:37.167
Chief Health Inspector
Mitchell Doily!

09:37.267 --> 09:39.200
I gotta talk to the manager!
- Excuse me!

09:39.300 --> 09:41.600
- Get up, Tubby.
- Sir, I'm the manager here.

09:41.700 --> 09:42.967
Could you bring it down
a little bit?

09:43.067 --> 09:44.433
- You're the manager?
Uh, uh, uh.

