to wash their hands

10:02.967 --> 10:04.900
after using the bathroom.

10:05.000 --> 10:07.300
- We had a soap dispenser
get ripped off the wall.

10:07.400 --> 10:09.133
- This place is getting
shut down for two weeks

10:09.233 --> 10:10.933
while we run
a thorough investigation.

10:11.033 --> 10:12.933
