Whoa, I just saw that.

10:17.133 --> 10:19.867
- I am in no way
trying to bribe you, sir.

10:19.967 --> 10:22.833
- Well, wait a second.

10:22.933 --> 10:25.633
Is that Burnin' Vernon Brown?

10:25.733 --> 10:29.367
