hottest newcomer of the year?

10:30.767 --> 10:32.067
- Yeah.

10:32.167 --> 10:34.400
- I've always wanted
to see that legend play live.

10:34.500 --> 10:35.900
Tell you what we can do.

10:36.000 --> 10:38.367
